content: ….The State Department put a bounty on Maduro for $15 Million Dollars, but Crazy Kamala and Crooked Joe are paying him BILLIONS OF DOLLARS for his Oil, instead of using our own, which is much better. America needs a STRONG Leader. People who need Peace and Freedom from Tyranny around the World depend on it. MAGA2024!
